transposes to 11.Be3.}) 12... Kf8 13. Bf4 Bxf4 14. Nxf4 g5 15. Bd3 Bg6 16. Bxg6
(16. Nxg6+ hxg6 17. Kf1 Nb6 $146 {Black has normal game.}) 16... hxg6 17. Nd3
g4 $5 $146 {I believe it's important to fix white's pawns. Now it will be
difficult for White to play h3 or f3 because it will damages his pawn
