1. e4 c6 2. d4 d5 3. Nc3 dxe4 4. Nxe4 Nf6 5. Nxf6+ exf6 6. Nf3 Bd6 7. Bd3 (7.
g3 O-O 8. Bg2 Re8+ 9. Be3 Qb6 10. O-O (10. Qc1 Qa6 {White has difficulties
