d6 and easy development.}) 12... Qe7 13. Rad1 Rd8 14. Qh5 b6 {[%cal Gc8b7]} 15.
Nd4 g6 $1 {[%cal Gc8b7,Gd6e5,Gf6f5,Yf8e6] Black has no problems.}) 11... Ng6 {
The following is a nice model game by Black:} 12. Rfe1 Bg4 13. h3 Be6 14. Rad1
