Poormosavi,S (2218)-Vishnu,P (2510) Sharjah UAE 2018}) (9. Be3 Re8 10. c4 Nd7
11. h3 Bh5 {, and another good game by Black:} 12. a3 c5 (12... Nf8 $5 $146 {
