have any problems out of the opening. White's Knight on c3 is somewhat
misplaced. Sooner or later White will probably have to play Ne4, which will
lead to more exchanges - suiting Black, who has slightly less space.}) 6... e6
7. d3 Nbd7 8. h3 b5 $5 $146 9. Bb3 a5 {[%cal Ga5a4]} 10. a4 Nc5 {[%csl Rb3]}
