{[#] White is planning to build a strong center by means of d2-d4 and c2-c4.
How should Black react?} 7... Bf5 $1 {This is a very important move to
remember. The idea to exchange the queens by means of ...Qe4 is thematic in
this line.} 8. c4 Qe4 9. d3 Qxe3+ 10. fxe3 Nd7 {Black equalized easily.} *

